My colleagues and I are the team of prosecutors working on the Jeffrey Epstein investigation, and 
we wondered if we might be able to set up a call with you for sometime this week, to ask you some logistical questions 
we're hoping you might either be able to answer or to point us in the right direction on. Would that be possible? If 
there are a few times in the coming days that you're free, we can try to figure out a slot that works for everyone. 
Thanks very much, and looking forward to being in touch.
